  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2017-05-16T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Strengthen And Fortify Existing Bridges Act of 2017 or the SAFE Bridges Act of 2017 \n\n This bill directs the Department of Transportation to establish a program to assist states to rehabilitate or replace bridges found to be structurally deficient.\n\nStates shall use apportioned program funds for projects to rehabilitate and replace such bridges.\n\nThe federal share of project costs is 100%.\n\nPrevailing rate of wage requirements for construction of federal-aid highways projects shall apply to such projects."
  }, 
